# CTA and Button Copy

- **Never use bracketed text** like `[ BUTTON ]` or `[ PROCEED ]` for call-to-action elements. It reads as gimmicky and unprofessional.
- Use standard, professional phrasing: "Login", "Register", "Submit", "Continue", etc.
- Prefer sentence case or title case for buttons; avoid all-caps unless it fits the design system.
